thread.title: Leigh Stone
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Leigh Stone

author: Leigh Stone
title: Leigh Stone
text:
easy to navigate online, printed the paperwork out, date and approximate time of pickup was given and the delivery date, wasn't that expensive.
Email was sent once the parcel had been delivered to the recipient
Highly recommend this company for sending parcels. Will definitely use this company again
Keep up the good work
